        "authorId" : "5102da93-31fa-41e6-b5fa-7de04e55f6ea",
        "body" : "I agree completely.  I understand it in the build section as necessary to activate features.  It may not be necessary - but that's how I understand it.\n\nThe whole scheme of vc features needs an overhaul.\n",
        "createdAt" : "2016-04-14T17:35:52Z",
