        "authorId" : "a3f1fdb0-47ad-411e-b63d-af6fc71a1fa6",
        "body" : "I was thinking about creating a `vc` quasi-metapackage that is versioned and builds off of the python system. Once we have it, we could actually pin the `vc` version directly with the package instead.\n",
        "createdAt" : "2016-04-14T17:37:48Z",
