        "authorId" : "5102da93-31fa-41e6-b5fa-7de04e55f6ea",
        "body" : "Yeah, looking at the error here is that you need a way to activate the feature.  Currently, only Python has the track_features - that's why it is necessary.  The version pinning is confusing because it is not pinned for the test section AFAIK.\n\nWe need metapackages for the track features.  I think these would only be used in tests.  In actual runtime environments, whatever executable is using the library should define track_features.\n",
